                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for deeply separating iron in silicate phase by depolymerizing iron silicate alkali and coupling hydrogen'reduction-magnetization '",
                    "一种硅酸铁碱解聚耦合氢“还原-磁化”深度分离硅酸盐相中铁的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for deeply separating iron in a silicate phase through'reduction-magnetization 'of iron silicate alkali depolymerization coupling hydrogen, and belongs to the field of solid waste resource utilization. The method comprises the following steps: (1) carrying out alkali depolymerization on ferric silicate; and (2) depolymerized slag hydrogen is subjected to'reduction-magnetization 'to deeply separate iron in a silicate phase. According to the method, NaOH is selected as a depolymerizing agent of ferric silicate, efficient depolymerization (products are Na2FeSiO4 and Fe2O3) of a silicate phase is achieved, meanwhile, hydrogen serves as a reducing agent to replace coke with large carbon emission, the metal recovery efficiency is guaranteed, meanwhile, the resource, energy and environment problems confronted by treatment of metal-containing solid waste are solved, and sustainable development of the industry is promoted. The whole technological process realizes low-pollution, carbon-free and economical industrial production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种硅酸铁碱解聚耦合氢“还原‑磁化”深度分离硅酸盐相中铁的方法，属于固体废物资源化利用领域。该方法包括以下步骤(1)硅酸铁碱解聚；(2)解聚渣氢“还原‑磁化”深度分离硅酸盐相中铁。本发明选用NaOH为硅酸铁的解聚剂，实现硅酸盐相的高效解聚(产物为Na2FeSiO4，Fe2O3)，同时用氢气作为还原剂替代碳排放量大的焦炭，保证金属回收效率的同时，改善含金属类固废处理所面临的资源、能源和环境问题，推动行业的可持续发展。整个工艺过程实现了低污染、无碳经济的工业化生产。"
                }
            ]
        }
